{"path":"records/concepts/trust-region-methods.md","type":"concept","summary":"Policy-gradient methods that bound how far each update moves the policy — TRPO via a KL trust region, PPO via a clipped ratio — to keep learning stable","tags":["reinforcement-learning","policy-gradient","trust-region","trpo","ppo"],"links":[],"created":"2026-04-23T16:00:00Z","updated":"2026-05-23T15:35:00Z","derived_from":["[[records/papers/schulman-trpo-2015]]","[[records/papers/schulman-ppo-2017]]"],"id":"trust-region-methods","meta-type":"conclusion","topic":"trust-region-methods"}
